## When user says 部署 / 上線 / 更新官網

1. Edit copy in `content/*.js` (anselbi) or `index.html` (ariel) as needed.
2. `npm run build` locally if you want to verify.
3. Commit + push `main` (or ask which repo).
4. CI deploys automatically; or `gh workflow run "Deploy to Cloudflare Pages" --repo Ans1lBBB/<repo>`.
5. Confirm: Actions green, site HTTP 200, anselbi has `cloudflareinsights` in HTML when analytics OK.

